Fig. 6A–D
). Pars comunis with conical microsculptures. Gonapophyses 8 and 9 with folds bearing conical microsculptures (
Figs 6E, F
, 
7A
). Thickenings of gonapophyses 9 present. Thickening of vaginal intima subrectangular (
